com.hazelcast.map.impl.mapstore.writebehind.entry

Interface DelayedEntry<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - the key type.
    V - the value type.

    public interface DelayedEntry<K,V>
    General contract for an entry to be stored into MapStore when MapStoreConfig.writeDelaySeconds is greater than 0.
    See Also:
    AddedDelayedEntry, DeletedDelayedEntry, NullValueDelayedEntry
